                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d289">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Chargé
                            <persName type="to">Bailey</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-05-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 10, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Root directs Mr. Bailey to express to the Nicaraguan Government, by
                    telegraph, this Government’s sympathy in the loss Nicaragua has sustained in the
                    assassination of its minister of foreign affairs, and its abhorrence of the
                    atrocious deed.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
